# Tentai VI - Quickstart Guide

## Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ 
- npm 9+

## 5-Minute Setup

### 1. Navigate to project
```bash
cd core/vi
```

### 2. Clean install (first time or after major changes)
```bash
rm -r node_modules dist package-lock.json  # macOS/Linux
# OR
rmdir /s node_modules dist package-lock.json  # Windows
```

### 3. Install dependencies
```bash
npm install
```

### 4. Type-check
```bash
npm run type-check
```

### 5. Build
```bash
npm run build
```

### 6. Start server
```bash
npm start
```
Server runs on `http://localhost:3001`

### 7. Use CLI (new terminal)
```bash
npm run cli -- --version
npm run cli -- help
```

